    \label{fig:viability_map}
\end{figure}

To generate a focused list for experimental consideration, we filtered the ranked candidates, selecting only those designated as purely theoretical and lying within the accessible energy window ($E_{hull} \le 0.05$ eV/atom). The top 10 prioritized candidates from this screening are presented in Table \ref{tab:top_candidates}.

